<h1>Flatiron School</h1>
<h3>Every story has heroes.</h3>

<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Name &nbsp;|</th>
    <th>Image &nbsp;|</th>
    <th>Tagline &nbsp;|</th>
    <th>Twitter &nbsp;|</th>
    <th>Linkedin &nbsp;|</th>
    <th>Github &nbsp;|</th>
    <th>Blog &nbsp;|</th>
